message: 'package' should be separated from previous statement.
Using the '.*' form of import should be avoided - java.io.*.
Wrong lexicographical order for 'java.io.*' import. Should be before 'org.junit.jupiter.api.Test'.
Wrong lexicographical order for 'java.nio.charset.StandardCharsets' import. Should be before 'org.junit.jupiter.api.Test'.
Import statement for 'org.junit.jupiter.api.Assertions.assertEquals' is in the wrong order. Should be in the 'STATIC' group, expecting not assigned imports on this line.
WhitespaceAround: 'for' is not followed by whitespace. Empty blocks may only be represented as {} when not part of a multi-block statement (4.1.3)
